{"tid":1444592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求所有盾牌「唔可以」加上習大大圖像","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:44.000Z","uid":40097,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f695050d3bf733303cd3138478bb2eff81a5383","tid":1444592,"uid":40097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"自從警察先生屌尻張建宗<br />\n已經有風吹出黎話習大大驚警察先生擁兵自重<br />\n如果佢打落去有習大大圖像既盾既話 <br />\n一定全世界都知警察先生落尻中央面<br />\n<br />\n同埋宜家盛傳有武警落左黎扮警察先生 雖然未fc<br />\n但係佢地見到習大大一定窒左下先<br />\n<br />\n總而言之示威者<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以</span></span>加習大大個樣上去佢地既防衛用具上面<br />\n如果唔係 會搞到警察先生止唔到亂 抗唔到暴架<br />\n佢地會好混淆架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止</span></span>佢地咁做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7934d432ea4d594cdae00e73b128431cc8694152","tid":1444592,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"大家記住唔可以呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7aee1da6cdee0797e082521f8ef120459690e9f","tid":1444592,"uid":191275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"唔可以！"},{"pid":"d14f395cc9d600803c30244a9a61b73135d80f4d","tid":1444592,"uid":54876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"唔好玩呢啲膠，係侮辱義士、烈士及死士"},{"pid":"e2f142c3a11837e556c7ee876a689d7f9633427d","tid":1444592,"uid":40097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d14f395cc9d600803c30244a9a61b73135d80f4d","tid":1444592,"uid":54876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"唔好玩呢啲膠，係侮辱義士、烈士及死士"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:53:33.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n咁樣做唯一<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好處</span></span>就係可以話比全世界知示威者效忠於中國 對中國有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我都唔知點好啦！！大家覺得點啊！！！不如討論下！！"},{"pid":"a0a73523a2a616959c313d8f87da5b0d90b4742a","tid":1444592,"uid":111934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"而家玩哩啲膠根本無用"}]}